The post office.


19 Apr 2010 06:27






This one I got the idea from when finishing up Ear Candles. The notion of an "Undead Letter Office" just seemed so fitting, but I wanted this to be different than other things out there. I was concerned about the similarities to the "New Pie" from Pratchett's Going Postal, but this place is significantly different from that. Photo started really liking the outline when we were chatting about it, and so here it is.

I hope you enjoy it.







